# Thuto Project Rules

## Tech Stack
- Framework: Next.js 15 (App Router)
- Database: Firebase Firestore
- Styling: Tailwind CSS
- Language: TypeScript

## General Principles
- Always use 'use client' directives only where necessary.
- Follow Botswana marking standards (e.g., ABCDE scales) for all grading logic.
- Ensure all components are mobile-responsive for school tablets.

## Database Safety
- Never modify Firestore security rules without explicit permission.
- Always use the Firebase instance located in src/lib/firebase.ts.
- DO NOT commit service-account.json or .env files.

## Deployment
- All code must pass 'npm run build' before being committed.
- App Hosting configuration is handled via apphosting.yaml.
